1729561,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"好大火"},{"pid":"ab1526786b90829c6498b6c18338afbe996d0245","tid":1729561,"uid":7327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1379a9288caf0b429ae92a84eb39eb8a400af725","tid":1729561,"uid":338712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"以上次中大一戰作參考，晚上有好大機會發生激烈衝突，加上popo經上次一役之後，戰術必有改善，<br />\n<br />\n而且中大一戰，popo只派一水炮車，<br />\n對比今次(一水炮、二鋭武、音波炮），而且旺角與poly非常近，所以加上旺角警力，可説popo今次差唔多總動員到poly<br />\n<br />\n另外學校報警、示威者取危險物品、使用弓箭、巨型亞叉等，popo可以此藉口，全面進入校園拘捕或使用致命武力。這必令各手足有慘重傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為popo正等待夜晚，街上人流減少，然後開戰。<br />\n<br />\n各前線手足，如果popo有任何唔妥，請唔好留，唔好送頭，唔好受傷，我哋一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n其他人，可選擇各區花、到中環集會或到poly支援。"},{"pid":"0396bd91bdcf49b2070e69fe23493274605c6c39","tid":1729561,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202320f8136f38275361e1dc29537732f4e9c24e","tid":1729561,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b448fc556a0a344f5a8f53b8546b3e79f3e5df","tid":1729561,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:04:24.000Z","msg":"手足們萬事小心"},{"pid":"dde21ce2c73ca5513e093fddd1722015c7e1418a","tid":1729561,"uid":237627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"救poly呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 